ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectEx Gratia Payments - Canadian Youth Business Foundation
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Canadian Heritage to make a one-time ex gratia payment of $100,000 to the Canadian Youth Business Foundation, to fund the program entitled The Prince's Operation Entrepreneur, on behalf of Their Royal Highnesses the Prince of Wales and the Duchess of Cornwall.
